'''J. Gause''' is a paramedic in Seattle.

==History==
Gause brought [[Lily (Hotter Than Hell)|Lily]] to the hospital with a serious pelvic injury after falling off a jetski. ''("[[Hotter Than Hell]]")''

After the gas main explosion, he brought in Vic and presented her case. ''("[[Bottle Up and Explode!]]")''

He later brought [[Alice Tom]] to the hospital after she was attacked at a bus stop for being Asian-American. ''("[[Stronger Than Hate]]")''

On Halloween, Gause brought in [[Jarah Al-Hasan]], a teen who had jumped off the roof while using LSD. ''("[[Haunted]]")''

==Career==
He is a paramedic in Seattle.
